                <fr:title text="Pointwise addition of matrices">Pointwise addition of <fr:link href="/jms-00IS/" title="Matrix over a semiring" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00IS/" display-uri="jms-00IS" type="local">matrices</fr:link></fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[M,N\in \mathrm {Mat}_{S}{\mathopen {}\left (m,n\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> be two <fr:link href="/jms-00IS/" title="Matrix over a semiring" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00IS/" display-uri="jms-00IS" type="local">matrices</fr:link> over the same semiring with the same dimensions. We will write <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[M\oplus  N\in \mathrm {Mat}_{S}{\mathopen {}\left (m,n\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> for the <html:em><html:strong>(pointwise) addition</html:strong></html:em> of the two matrices:</html:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
 {\mathopen {}\left (M\oplus  N\right )\mathclose {}}_{i,j} = M_{i,j} \oplus  N_{i,j}
]]></fr:tex>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
