                <fr:title text="Associativity, commutativity, and unit laws of matrix addition">Associativity, commutativity, and unit laws of <fr:link href="/jms-00JO/" title="Pointwise addition of matrices" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00JO/" display-uri="jms-00JO" type="local">matrix addition</fr:link></fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Matrix addition forms an associative and commutative operation on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathrm {Mat}_{S}{\mathopen {}\left (m,n\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> with zero matrices <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {0}]]></fr:tex> as neutral element.</html:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>1</fr:month><fr:day>20</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>This follows immediately from the associativity, commutativity, and unit laws of the additive submonoid <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (+,0\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> of the semiring <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
</fr:mainmatter>
